article_id:171,category_name:News,title_name:About the Treasure Trade Update,image_path:,message:<div>The Treasure Trade menu will be updated around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1545888600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>During the update process, attempting to trade something in the Treasure Trade menu may cause errors and send users back to the title screen.</div><div>In this case, the attempted trades will not be carried out.</div><div><br></div><div>We will notify you of the details of this update in a separate announcement.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1545886800,update_time1545887917